Net-Abuse-Utils version 0.04
==============================

This module provides functions to lookup information about an IP or
ASN.

Data available includes:
	* country code for an IP or ASN
	* ASN announcing an IP via BGP
	* CIDR network an IP is announced in
	* contact email addresses based on IP whois info
	* contact email addresses for a domain based on abuse.net data
	* contact email address from the SOA record for the rDNS zone for an IP
	* listing information for an IP in a specific DNSBL

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:
	Net::DNS, Net::Whois::IP, Email::Address

